// ----------------------------------------------------------------
// -------------------------swizzle layout-------------------------
// --------------------logical col 0~64, step 8--------------------
// ---------------------smem col 0~16, step 8----------------------
// ----------------------------------------------------------------
// |bank  |b 0~3 |b 4~7 |b 0~3 |b 4~7 |b 0~3 |b 4~7 |b 0~3 |b 4~7 |
// |row 0 |  0   |  8   |  0   |  8   |  0   |  8   |  0   |  8   |
// |bank  |b 8~11|b12~15|b 8~11|b12~15|b 8~11|b12~15|b 8~11|b12~15|
// |row 1 |  0   |  8   |  0   |  8   |  0   |  8   |  0   |  8   |
